<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Confirmaci√≥n de Pedido</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: #333;
      background-color: #f4f4f4;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
    }
    .container {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 20px auto;
      background-color: #ffffff;
      border-radius: 8px;
      overflow: hidden;
      box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    }
    .header {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
      color: white;
      padding: 30px 20px;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .header h1 {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: 28px;
      font-weight: 600;
    }
    .content {
      padding: 30px 20px;
    }
    .greeting {
      font-size: 18px;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      color: #333;
    }
    .order-id {
      background-color: #f8f9fa;
      padding: 15px;
      border-radius: 6px;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      border-left: 4px solid #667eea;
    }
    .order-id strong {
      color: #667eea;
    }
    .section {
      margin-bottom: 25px;
    }
    .section-title {
      font-size: 16px;
      font-weight: 600;
      color: #667eea;
      margin-bottom: 12px;
      border-bottom: 2px solid #e9ecef;
      padding-bottom: 8px;
    }
    .file-list {
      list-style: none;
      padding: 0;
      margin: 0;
    }
    .file-item {
      background-color: #f8f9fa;
      padding: 12px;
      margin-bottom: 8px;
      border-radius: 4px;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
    }
    .file-name {
      font-weight: 500;
      color: #333;
    }
    .file-pages {
      color: #6c757d;
      font-size: 14px;
    }
    .options-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
      gap: 12px;
      margin-bottom: 15px;
    }
    .option-item {
      background-color: #f8f9fa;
      padding: 12px;
      border-radius: 4px;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .option-label {
      font-size: 12px;
      color: #6c757d;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.5px;
      margin-bottom: 4px;
    }
    .option-value {
      font-size: 16px;
      font-weight: 600;
      color: #333;
    }
    .pickup-info {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea15 0%, #764ba215 100%);
      padding: 20px;
      border-radius: 8px;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      border: 2px solid #667eea;
    }
    .pickup-info .icon {
      font-size: 24px;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }
    .pickup-info h3 {
      margin: 0 0 15px 0;
      color: #667eea;
      font-size: 18px;
    }
    .pickup-details {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-around;
      gap: 15px;
    }
    .pickup-detail {
      flex: 1;
      text-align: center;
      background-color: white;
      padding: 12px;
      border-radius: 6px;
    }
    .pickup-detail-label {
      font-size: 12px;
      color: #6c757d;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      margin-bottom: 4px;
    }
    .pickup-detail-value {
      font-size: 18px;
      font-weight: 600;
      color: #667eea;
    }
    .total-price {
      background-color: #667eea;
      color: white;
      padding: 20px;
      border-radius: 8px;
      text-align: center;
      margin: 20px 0;
    }
    .total-price .label {
      font-size: 14px;
      opacity: 0.9;
      margin-bottom: 5px;
    }
    .total-price .amount {
      font-size: 36px;
      font-weight: 700;
    }
    .comment-box {
      background-color: #fff3cd;
      border-left: 4px solid #ffc107;
      padding: 15px;
      border-radius: 4px;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }
    .comment-box strong {
      color: #856404;
    }
    .cta-button {
      display: inline-block;
      background-color: #667eea;
      color: white !important;
      text-decoration: none;
      padding: 14px 32px;
      border-radius: 6px;
      font-weight: 600;
      text-align: center;
      margin: 20px 0;
      transition: background-color 0.3s;
    }
    .cta-button:hover {
      background-color: #5568d3;
    }
    .footer {
      background-color: #f8f9fa;
      padding: 20px;
      text-align: center;
      color: #6c757d;
      font-size: 14px;
    }
    .footer p {
      margin: 5px 0;
    }
    @media only screen and (max-width: 600px) {
      .options-grid {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      }
      .pickup-details {
        flex-direction: column;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <h1>‚úÖ Pedido Confirmado</h1>
    </div>

    <div class="content">
      <p class="greeting">Hola <strong>{{userName}}</strong>,</p>

      <div class="order-id">
        <strong>Pedido:</strong> #{{orderId}}
      </div>

      <p>Tu pedido ha sido recibido con √©xito y est√° siendo procesado. A continuaci√≥n encontrar√°s los detalles de tu orden:</p>

      <!-- Files Section -->
      <div class="section">
        <div class="section-title">üìÑ Archivos</div>
        <ul class="file-list">
          {{#each files}}
          <li class="file-item">
            <span class="file-name">{{this.originalName}}</span>
            <span class="file-pages">{{this.pages}} p√°gina{{#if (gt this.pages 1)}}s{{/if}}</span>
          </li>
          {{/each}}
        </ul>
      </div>

      <!-- Options Section -->
      <div class="section">
        <div class="section-title">‚öôÔ∏è Opciones de Impresi√≥n</div>
        <div class="options-grid">
          <div class="option-item">
            <div class="option-label">Tama√±o</div>
            <div class="option-value">{{options.size}}</div>
          </div>
          <div class="option-item">
            <div class="option-label">Cantidad</div>
            <div class="option-value">{{options.quantity}}</div>
          </div>
          <div class="option-item">
            <div class="option-label">Color</div>
            <div class="option-value">{{#if options.isColor}}A Color{{else}}Blanco y Negro{{/if}}</div>
          </div>
          <div class="option-item">
            <div class="option-label">Impresi√≥n</div>
            <div class="option-value">{{#if options.isDuplex}}Doble Faz{{else}}Simple Faz{{/if}}</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Pickup Information (if available) -->
      {{#if hasPickupInfo}}
      <div class="pickup-info">
        <div class="icon">üìÖ</div>
        <h3>Informaci√≥n de Retiro</h3>
        <div class="pickup-details">
          <div class="pickup-detail">
            <div class="pickup-detail-label">Fecha</div>
            <div class="pickup-detail-value">{{pickupDate}}</div>
          </div>
          <div class="pickup-detail">
            <div class="pickup-detail-label">Hora</div>
            <div class="pickup-detail-value">{{pickupTime}}</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      {{/if}}

      <!-- Comment (if available) -->
      {{#if comment}}
      <div class="comment-box">
        <strong>üí¨ Comentario:</strong> {{comment}}
      </div>
      {{/if}}

      <!-- Total Price -->
      <div class="total-price">
        <div class="label">Total Estimado</div>
        <div class="amount">${{totalPrice}}</div>
      </div>

      <p style="text-align: center;">
        <a href="{{frontendUrl}}/orders" class="cta-button">Ver Mis Pedidos</a>
      </p>

      <p style="font-size: 14px; color: #6c757d; text-align: center;">
        üí° Los precios son estimados y pueden variar seg√∫n disponibilidad
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="footer">
      <p><strong>Gr√°fica System</strong></p>
      <p>Lunes a S√°bados | 8:00 AM - 5:00 PM</p>
      <p>¬øNecesitas ayuda? Cont√°ctanos respondiendo a este email.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
